org.smartclean.globalUtility.requestUtil.WFM

Class WFMMainRequestObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.smartclean.globalUtility.requestUtil.WFM.WFMMainRequestObject

  • public class WFMMainRequestObject
extends Object
    Main requestObject wrapper class with all the required fields for making api calls to the endpoints hosted under workforce-management module. Class contains static methods to return instances of itself with mandatory variables populated. Property variables have getter functions annotated with JsonProperty names to facilitate deterministic marshalling/unmarshalling of Object and its JSON format.
